# <Multi_key> <l> <f> : "( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)"        # Lenny face
# <Multi_key> <s> <f> : "¯\\_(ツ)_/¯"     # Shrug face

### My additions
#
#### Slightly easier eñe
<Multi_key> <n> <n> : "ñ"
<Multi_key> <N> <N> : "Ñ"

#### More intuitive card suits (instead of 3-, E>, and 33 for ♠, ♥, and ♣, and no shortcut for ♦)
##### First, override the "white diamond suit" currently assigned to <Compose> < >
<Multi_key> <less> <greater> : "♦"
##### Then give both shorter and longer versions that might be easier to remember
<Multi_key> <s> <u> <i> <t> <s> : "♠"
<Multi_key> <s> <u> <i> <t> <h> : "♥"
<Multi_key> <s> <u> <i> <t> <d> : "♦"
<Multi_key> <s> <u> <i> <t> <c> : "♣"
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <s> <p> <a> <d> <e> <s> : "♠"
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <h> <e> <a> <r> <t> <s> : "♥"
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <d> <i> <a> <m> <o> <n> <d> <s> : "♦"
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <c> <l> <u> <b> <s> : "♣"

#### PlayStation symbols (via Geometric Shapes)
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <j> : "✕"
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <k> : "○"
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <u> : "□"
<Multi_key> <Multi_key> <i> : "△"

#### Compose key
<Multi_key> <c> <m> <p> <s> : "⎄"
